  "mwindo-underworld": {
    "en": [
      "Mwindo in the Underworld is best understood within the storytelling traditions of Democratic Republic of the Congo in Central Africa. It stays anchored in hero, trial, and honor rather than in a single fixed version. It is most useful as a guide to the themes of hero, trial, and honor. That keeps the story tied to landscape, community, and transmission from the start.",
      "As an epic-facing entry, it gathers attention around hero, trial, and the kind of trial that tests standing or endurance. The emphasis falls on remembered scale, heroic pressure, and the path a community keeps worth retelling. Even where versions differ, the story usually persists because it carries honor, ordeal, and movement across a larger world. That larger frame matters more than pretending we already have every episode pinned down.",
      "Here Mwindo in the Underworld serves as a regional memory of what counts as greatness, burden, or costly achievement in Democratic Republic of the Congo in Central Africa. It also keeps the relation between hero, route, and audience in view. The motifs of hero, trial, and honor do the real structural work. What endures is the scale of the ordeal and the memory of who was judged equal to it."
    ],
    "zh": [
      "《姆温多下冥界》最好先放回中非的刚果民主共和国的讲述传统里来理解。这条叙述把重心落在“英雄”“试炼”和“荣誉”这些意象上，而不是单一固定版本上。它更适合被读作关于“英雄”“试炼”“荣誉”的地方讲述。因此开头就把地点、社群和传承方式一起摆了出来。",
      "如果把它放在史诗的尺度上看，视线自然会集中到“英雄”“试炼”和必须承受的试炼上。这类条目保存的往往是英雄压力、远行规模和社群愿意反复讲述的壮阔感。哪怕细节版本有差异，荣誉、磨难和行路通常仍是骨架。真正重要的是那种被记成“大事”的结构，而不是假装已经掌握全部桥段。",
      "因此《姆温多下冥界》在这里保存的是中非的刚果民主共和国关于伟业、重负与代价的记忆。它也让英雄、路线和听众之间的关系继续可见。支撑整条叙述的，其实是“英雄”“试炼”“荣誉”这些母题。最后被记住的，是试炼的尺度，以及谁被认为配得上承受它。"
    ]
  },
